    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> if you encounter this error on another project, it's because the version used by default by yarn is old and has a bug with post install of npm packages. To solve this you need to specify the version of Yarn using a environment variable on netlify: YARN_VERSION\r\n\r\nThanks for this",
